title: Israeli defense minister on Hamas, ground operations: 'Not looking for bigger wars'
description: When asked about the impending ground operation into Gaza, Israeli Defense Minister Yoav Gallant told ABC News: "We are close. You'll hear it one minute after Hamas."

title: Off-duty deputy shoots man in Omaha, Nebraska, leading to hospitalization
description: Authorities say a man shot by an off-duty deputy in Omaha, Nebraska, over the weekend is in serious but stable condition with a gunshot wound to the chest

title: Russians commemorate victims of Soviet repression as a present-day crackdown on dissent intensifies
description: Putin's government continues its crackdown on dissent in the country.

title: 4 people, including 2 students, shot near Atlanta college campus
description: Police said the shooting stemmed from a dispute between two groups.

title: WATCH:  Crash on highway causes unintentional fireworks show
description: A semitruck collided with a pickup truck carrying fireworks, causing the fireworks to ignite, according to reports. One person was reportedly hospitalized.

title: Thousands of Ukrainians run to commemorate those killed in the war
description: Around 2,000 Ukrainians have taken part in a one-kilometer race in Kyiv.

title: 2 dead, 18 injured in Tampa street shooting, police say
description: A shooting that broke out in a Tampa neighborhood has killed two people and injured another 18, according to police.

title: Man charged in killing of Nat King Cole's great-nephew
description: Investigators have charged Ricardo Gayle, 41, with his killing.

title: Shooting kills 2 and injures 18 victims in Florida street
description: A fight between two groups turned deadly during Halloween festivities.

title: 1 dead, 8 others injured in shooting at large party in Indianapolis
description: One person is dead and eight others are injured after a shooting at a large party in Indianapolis, Indiana, early Sunday morning, police said.

title: American hockey player Adam Johnson dies after 'freak accident' during game in England
description: American hockey player Adam Johnson has died after a “freak accident” during a game in England on Saturday, his club said

title: Russia says it shot down 36 Ukrainian drones as fighting grinds on in Ukraine’s east
description: Russia’s Defense Ministry says its air defense shot down 36 Ukrainian drones over the Black Sea and the Crimean peninsula overnight Saturday

title: Alleged Maine gunman tried to buy a silencer months before Lewiston shootings
description: The alleged Maine gunman, Robert Card, tried to buy a silencer for a rifle at a local firearms store three months prior to the mass shooting, the owner said Saturday.

title: WATCH:  Matthew Perry, star of 'Friends,' dies at 54: Sources
description: The actor was known for playing Chandler Bing on the hit ensemble sitcom "Friends," which ran from 1994 to 2004.

title: 'Friends' star Matthew Perry dies at 54: Sources
description: Matthew Perry has died at the age of 54, according to law enforcement sources.
